## Composing a High-Level System Definition

While not my intent, this writing returned me to the framework of a [Parts, Products, and People](/articles/picking-parts-products-people.html) workshop I’ve run for years. This activity steps participants through a prescribed protocol to detail what parts their system needs, what products it’ll apply to, and who does the work.

{% endfilter %}

  {{ escom.article_figure(
